com.ardock.moodapp.moodgen.lib.ui.utils

Class SliderTabHelper

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ardock.moodapp.moodgen.lib.ui.utils.BaseTabHelper
      • com.ardock.moodapp.moodgen.lib.ui.utils.SliderTabHelper
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    MaterialTabHelper

    public abstract class SliderTabHelper
extends BaseTabHelper
    SliderTabHelper is a slider helper class for your project that: save/load/reset the extra settings preferences. save/load/reset the utils preferences. Get/Set an util preference. Inherited: Get the previous tabview position of the actual position. save/load/reset the base settings preferences. Get/Set a setting preference.
